Union MaybeI32 has none; some value: i32.

To choose maybe flag: i1, giving MaybeI32.
Give match flag:
true gives MaybeI32.some with value be 9;
false gives MaybeI32.none;
otherwise gives MaybeI32.none.

To main, giving i32.
Let maybe be choose maybe true.
Give match maybe:
MaybeI32.some with value gives value;
otherwise gives 0.
